LIBRARY GENGRADD
DESCRIPTION 'VirtualBox GRADD (C) 2007-2026 Oracle and/or its affiliates'
PROTMODE
CODE PRELOAD
DATA PRELOAD
SEGMENTS
    DATA_SHARED CLASS 'DATA' SHARED READWRITE ; Why is the tradition 'READONLY' here?
EXPORTS
    HWEntry @1
IMPORTS
    VMAN.VHAllocMem
    VMAN.VHFreeMem
    VMAN.VHLockMem
    VMAN.VHMapVRAM
    VIDEOPMI.VIDEOPMI32Request

